#<AdxTL>@(#)0.0.0.0 $Revision$
# Superviseur
# Gestion du masque DLA1 

$_AFF
If GIMPORT
 Gosub AFF From GSAISIE
Else
 If GMESSAGE <>""
  Gosub ERR From GSAISIE
 Else
  Raz GERR , GZNUM
 Endif
Endif
Return

$HORODAT
Local Date    A_DATE
Local Char    A_HEURE(10) , A_USER(10)
Local Char    A_STAMP(15)
A_DATE  = [09/11/2018]
A_HEURE = "23:03:58"
A_USER  = "DOC"
A_STAMP = "20181109230358"
Return

$TITRES
Chgtzn [M:DLA1]ADD1 With [F:TCY]ADRNAM(0)
Chgtzn [M:DLA1]ADD2 With [F:TCY]ADRNAM(1)
Chgtzn [M:DLA1]ADD3 With [F:TCY]ADRNAM(2)
Return

$VISU
Local Integer A_REPONSE
Global Integer GPRE_VIEW
If dim(A_WINDPREV)<=0 : Local Char A_WINDPREV(30) : Endif
Local Mask DLA1 [DLA1]
Gosub HORODAT
Local Inpbox "DLA1" From GFONCTION At A_STAMP With A_WINDPREV Mask [DLA1] As [SIM_]
Grizo [DLA1]5
Grizo [DLA1]10
Grizo [DLA1]20
Grizo [DLA1]30
Grizo [DLA1]35
Boxact [SIM_]
Gosub TITRES
Boxinp [SIM_] Using A_REPONSE
Close Local Inpbox [SIM_]
Close Local Mask [DLA1]
Kill GPRE_VIEW
Return

$HARDCOP
Local Integer X1(0..14),X2(0..14),Y1(0..14),Y2(0..14)
X1(0)=1 : X2(0)=97 : Y1(0)=1 : Y2(0)=5
X1(1)=1 : X2(1)=97 : Y1(1)=6 : Y2(1)=10
X1(2)=1 : X2(2)=97 : Y1(2)=11 : Y2(2)=14
X1(3)=1 : X2(3)=97 : Y1(3)=15 : Y2(3)=20
X1(4)=1 : X2(4)=97 : Y1(4)=21 : Y2(4)=25
Return

