$ON_CODPOS
Onevent BEFORE_AREA Gosub AV_CODPOS From W1DLA1
Onevent CONTROL Call C_CODPOS(zc) From W1DLA1
Onevent AFTER_CHANGE Gosub AMM_CODPOS From W1DLA1
Onevent BEFORE_INPUT Call AS_CODPOS(zc) From W1DLA1
Return

$AV_CODPOS
